Package: pestrPRA
Type: Package
Title: Bookdown Templates for Express Pest Risk Assessment (EPPO)
Version: 0.4.1
Author: person("Michal Jan", "Czyz", email = "m.czyz.j@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package contains RMarkdown templates to create Express Pest
